00:48:08,035 --> 00:48:10,037
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT?

498
00:48:11,538 --> 00:48:15,542
[MEEK VOICE]
OH, NO.

499
00:48:15,542 --> 00:48:17,544
I'M STILL GRATEFUL FOR LOVE.

500
00:48:20,547 --> 00:48:23,050
[FIRM VOICE]
WHAT DO YOU WANT, THEN?

501
00:48:28,055 --> 00:48:32,059
[MEEK VOICE]
I PRAY FOR JAN TO COME HOME.

502
00:48:34,561 --> 00:48:37,564
[FIRM VOICE]
HE WILL BE COMING HOME
IN 10 DAYS.

503
00:48:37,564 --> 00:48:40,567
YOU MUST LEARN TO ENDURE.
YOU KNOW THAT.

504
00:48:45,572 --> 00:48:48,075
[MEEK VOICE]
OH, I CAN'T WAIT.

505
00:48:53,580 --> 00:48:56,083
[FIRM VOICE]
THIS IS UNLIKE YOU, BESS.

506
00:48:56,083 --> 00:49:00,587
OUT THERE, THERE ARE PEOPLE
WHO NEED JAN AND HIS WORK.

507
00:49:00,587 --> 00:49:02,589
WHAT ABOUT THEM?

508
00:49:06,593 --> 00:49:12,099
[MEEK VOICE]
THEY DON'T MATTER.
NOTHING ELSE MATTERS.

509
00:49:12,099 --> 00:49:16,103
I JUST WANT JAN HOME AGAIN.

510
00:49:16,603 --> 00:49:19,106
I PRAY TO YOU.

511
00:49:19,106 --> 00:49:23,110
OH, PLEASE,
WON'T YOU SEND HIM HOME?

512
00:49:27,614 --> 00:49:31,618
[FIRM VOICE]
ARE YOU SURE
THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT?

513
00:49:36,123 --> 00:49:38,625
[MEEK VOICE]
YES.

514
00:50:03,817 --> 00:50:05,819
OK. GET HER UP.

515
00:50:16,329 --> 00:50:18,331
BLOW OUT!

516
00:50:18,331 --> 00:50:19,332
[ALARM BEEPING]

517
00:50:19,332 --> 00:50:21,334
GET AWAY!
BLOW OUT!

518
00:50:21,334 --> 00:50:22,836
TERRY!

519
00:50:22,836 --> 00:50:23,837
TERRY!

520
00:50:32,462 --> 00:50:33,964
TERRY! TERRY!

521
00:50:37,350 --> 00:50:38,351
TERRY!

522
00:50:44,725 --> 00:50:46,359
TALK TO ME, WILL YOU?

523
00:50:52,232 --> 00:50:54,234
[MAN YELLING]

524
00:51:04,745 --> 00:51:05,746
WATCH OUT!

525
00:51:07,380 --> 00:51:09,382
JAN!

526
00:51:09,382 --> 00:51:12,886
GO GET--GET A MEDIC!

527
00:51:31,772 --> 00:51:34,775
Minister: I DON'T KNOW
WHAT KIND OF CONDITION
HE'S IN.

528
00:51:34,775 --> 00:51:38,161
I THINK IT'S
VERY SERIOUS, THOUGH.

529
00:51:38,161 --> 00:51:40,163
I DON'T QUITE KNOW.

530
00:51:47,170 --> 00:51:50,674
IT'S JAN. THERE'S BEEN
AN ACCIDENT ON THE RIG.

531
00:52:41,341 --> 00:52:43,343
[HELICOPTER ENGINE
RUMBLING]

532
00:52:45,846 --> 00:52:48,348
JAN, CAN YOU HEAR ME?

533
00:52:52,853 --> 00:52:54,855
OH.

534
00:53:03,113 --> 00:53:05,115
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

535
00:53:05,115 --> 00:53:07,617
I'M HOLDING
YOUR HAND.

536
00:53:07,617 --> 00:53:09,119
DON'T TOUCH ME.

537
00:53:09,119 --> 00:53:10,620
DON'T TOUCH ME!

538
00:53:10,620 --> 00:53:12,122
Man: JAN, RELAX.
JUST TAKE...

539
00:53:25,385 --> 00:53:26,887
SIT DOWN HERE.

540
00:53:31,391 --> 00:53:33,894
ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT.

541
00:53:33,894 --> 00:53:36,396
SHH.
DEEP BREATH.

542
00:53:36,396 --> 00:53:38,899
HELLO. TALK
TO ME, DARLING.

543
00:53:38,899 --> 00:53:40,901
TALK TO ME.

544
00:53:40,901 --> 00:53:42,402
TALK TO ME.

545
00:53:42,903 --> 00:53:44,404
COME ON.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

546
00:53:46,907 --> 00:53:48,909
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
IT'S GOING TO BE
ALL RIGHT.

547
00:54:07,060 --> 00:54:09,062
UH, THEY'RE GOING
TO OPERATE STRAIGHTAWAY.

548
00:54:09,062 --> 00:54:11,564
IT WILL BE
A FEW HOURS,

549
00:54:12,065 --> 00:54:13,066
SO I THINK
WE BETTER WAIT...

550
00:54:13,066 --> 00:54:15,068
Dodo: BESS.

551
00:54:15,068 --> 00:54:18,071
BESS, YOU CAN'T
GO IN THERE.

552
00:54:18,071 --> 00:54:19,572
IT'S
NOT ALLOWED.
I WANT TO BE WITH HIM.

553
00:54:19,572 --> 00:54:20,573
I KNOW YOU DO.
I KNOW.

554
00:54:20,573 --> 00:54:21,574
BUT COME ON.
COME WITH ME.
COME ON.

555
00:54:21,574 --> 00:54:24,077
NO. I WANT TO SEE HIM
ALL THE TIME.

556
00:54:24,077 --> 00:54:27,080
BESS, IT'S NOT
A GOOD IDEA.
COME ON.

557
00:54:27,080 --> 00:54:30,083
BESS. BESS, PLEASE,
YOU CAN'T STAY HERE.

558
00:54:30,583 --> 00:54:32,085
IT'S JUST NOT POSSIBLE.

559
00:54:32,085 --> 00:54:33,086
BESS!

560
00:54:33,086 --> 00:54:35,088
CAN I HAVE
A WORD WITH YOU?

561
00:54:35,088 --> 00:54:38,591
STAY THERE,
ALL RIGHT?
DON'T MOVE.

562
00:55:00,981 --> 00:55:03,984
I WANT YOU
TO PRAY WITH ME.

563
00:55:06,987 --> 00:55:07,487
Dodo: BUT...

564
00:55:07,988 --> 00:55:09,489
PLEASE.

565
00:55:24,137 --> 00:55:28,641
DEAR GOD,
WE PRAY THAT YOU

566
00:55:29,142 --> 00:55:32,145
WILL HOLD YOUR HAND
OVER JAN

567
00:55:32,645 --> 00:55:36,149
AND NOT LET HIM DIE.

568
00:55:36,149 --> 00:55:37,650
[TOGETHER]
AMEN.

569
00:56:12,936 --> 00:56:16,439
MRS. NYMAN,
WILL YOU PLEASE
COME WITH ME?

570
00:56:45,969 --> 00:56:48,471
WILL HE LIVE?

571
00:56:48,471 --> 00:56:55,478
WE HAVE STABILIZED
YOUR HUSBAND'S CONDITION
FOR THE TIME BEING.

572
00:56:58,481 --> 00:57:00,984
WILL HE LIVE?

573
00:57:00,984 --> 00:57:03,987
YES. YES, BESS,
HE WILL LIVE.

574
00:57:11,995 --> 00:57:15,498
YOUR HUSBAND SUFFERED
VERY SERIOUS INJURIES.

575
00:57:17,500 --> 00:57:21,004
LIFE SHOULDN'T ALWAYS
BE PRESERVED AT ANY COST.

576
00:57:23,256 --> 00:57:25,258
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

577
00:57:28,261 --> 00:57:30,763
UM, WELL, THE DOCTOR
MEANS, BESS,

578
00:57:30,763 --> 00:57:34,767
THAT, UM, SOMETIMES...

579
00:57:35,268 --> 00:57:38,271
IN SOME CASES
WHEN LIFE ISN'T
WORTH LIVING,

580
00:57:38,271 --> 00:57:41,774
THEN IT MAY
BE BETTER TO DIE.

581
00:57:46,779 --> 00:57:52,785
YOU DON'T KNOW JAN,
OR YOU COULD NOT
SAY SUCH A THING.

582
00:57:54,287 --> 00:57:57,790
YOUR HUSBAND
MAY NEVER WALK AGAIN.

583
00:57:57,790 --> 00:58:01,294
WE THINK HE'LL BE
COMPLETELY PARALYZED.

584
00:58:03,296 --> 00:58:05,298
BUT HE'LL LIVE?

585
00:58:05,298 --> 00:58:09,302
YES. HE WILL LIVE,
IT SEEMS.

586
00:58:18,928 --> 00:58:20,563
[MEEK VOICE]
FATHER.

587
00:58:22,065 --> 00:58:24,567
ARE YOU THERE?

588
00:58:24,567 --> 00:58:26,569
ARE YOU STILL THERE?

589
00:58:31,074 --> 00:58:33,576
[FIRM VOICE]
OF COURSE I AM, BESS.

590
00:58:33,576 --> 00:58:35,078
YOU KNOW THAT.

591
00:58:44,587 --> 00:58:47,090
[MEEK VOICE]
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

592
00:58:52,595 --> 00:58:56,099
[FIRM VOICE]
YOU WANTED JAN HOME.

593
00:58:59,602 --> 00:59:02,105
[MEEK VOICE]
I'VE CHANGED MY MIND.

594
00:59:02,105 --> 00:59:04,107
WHY DID I ASK
FOR THAT?

595
00:59:07,110 --> 00:59:08,611
[FIRM VOICE]
BECAUSE YOU'RE

596
00:59:09,112 --> 00:59:11,614
A STUPID
LITTLE GIRL, BESS.

597
00:59:11,614 --> 00:59:14,617
I HAD TO TEST YOU.

598
00:59:14,617 --> 00:59:18,621
YOUR LOVE FOR JAN
HAS BEEN PUT TO THE TEST.

599
00:59:27,130 --> 00:59:28,631
[MEEK VOICE]
THANK YOU

600
00:59:28,631 --> 00:59:30,633
FOR NOT LETTING HIM DIE.

601
00:59:35,638 --> 00:59:37,640
[FIRM VOICE]
YOU'RE WELCOME, BESS.

602
00:59:53,273 --> 00:59:59,279
?? HE SAID
  "THERE IS NO REASON ??

603
00:59:59,279 --> 01:00:02,282
?? AND THE TRUTH
IS PLAIN TO SEE" ??

604
01:00:05,285 --> 01:00:09,289
?? BUT I WANDERED
THROUGH MY PLAYING CARDS ??

605
01:00:11,791 --> 01:00:15,295
?? AND WOULD NOT
LET HER BE ??

606
01:00:18,298 --> 01:00:22,302
?? ONE OF 16
VESTAL VIRGINS ??

607
01:00:24,804 --> 01:00:27,807
?? WHO WERE LEAVING
FOR THE COAST ??

608
01:00:31,311 --> 01:00:35,815
?? AND ALTHOUGH
MY EYES WERE OPEN ??

609
01:00:37,817 --> 01:00:41,321
?? THEY MIGHT JUST AS WELL
HAVE BEEN CLOSED ??

610
01:00:41,321 --> 01:00:43,823
?? AND SO IT WAS... ??

611
01:00:43,823 --> 01:00:47,827
Minister: I WOULD SAY TO YOU...

612
01:00:47,827 --> 01:00:51,331
THAT IF THERE IS
ONE OF THESE COMMANDMENTS

613
01:00:51,331 --> 01:00:56,836
WHICH YOU DO NOT LOVE
AND DO NOT OBEY,

614
01:00:56,836 --> 01:01:00,840
YOU HAVE NO PLACE
AT THE LORD'S TABLE.

615
01:01:00,840 --> 01:01:02,959
[SINGING HYMN]

616
01:01:25,481 --> 01:01:26,983
WHEN DID YOU
GET BACK?

617
01:01:26,983 --> 01:01:28,484
I CAME BACK
WITH JAN.

618
01:01:28,985 --> 01:01:30,987
OH, IT'S GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

619
01:01:46,302 --> 01:01:47,804
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

620
01:01:47,804 --> 01:01:50,673
OH, SURF'S UP!

621
01:01:50,673 --> 01:01:51,808
Pits: HI.

622
01:01:51,808 --> 01:01:52,809
Jan: HI, GUYS.

623
01:01:53,309 --> 01:01:54,310
Terry: HOW YOU DOING,
BUDDY?

624
01:01:54,310 --> 01:01:56,312
WELL, FINE.
HOW ARE YOU?

625
01:01:56,312 --> 01:01:57,814
OK.

626
01:02:00,817 --> 01:02:02,318
DID YOU FIND ANYTHING?

627
01:02:02,819 --> 01:02:04,320
Terry: GAS.

628
01:02:04,320 --> 01:02:05,822
NOTHING REALLY.

629
01:02:05,822 --> 01:02:07,824
HA HA!
GUESS WHAT, NOW.

630
01:02:07,824 --> 01:02:09,325
WE'RE HEADING UP NORTH.

631
01:02:09,325 --> 01:02:10,827
WELL, NORTH,
THAT'S GOOD.

632
01:02:11,327 --> 01:02:13,830
THAT'S WHERE YOU
ALWAYS SAID THE OIL WAS.

633
01:02:14,197 --> 01:02:16,199
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE, ANYWAY?

634
01:02:16,199 --> 01:02:18,201
WE'RE MEANT TO BE
OUT DRILLING.

635
01:02:18,201 --> 01:02:19,702
[OPENS CAN]

636
01:02:19,702 --> 01:02:21,204
Jan:
I JUST FELT LIKE

637
01:02:21,204 --> 01:02:23,706
PUTTING MY FEET UP
FOR A WHILE.

638
01:02:23,840 --> 01:02:27,343
I DIDN'T TRUST
YOU 2 GUYS
OUT THERE ALONE.

639
01:02:27,343 --> 01:02:29,345
[LAUGHTER]

640
01:02:29,345 --> 01:02:31,347
[CANS OPENING]

641
01:02:39,105 --> 01:02:41,107
OH, MY...

642
01:02:41,107 --> 01:02:44,110
MY ARMS AREN'T OK, SO...

643
01:02:44,110 --> 01:02:46,612
I'M NOT THIRSTY, ANYWAY.

644
01:02:48,614 --> 01:02:51,617
BULLSHIT!

645
01:02:55,738 --> 01:02:57,740
HEY, COME ON.

646
01:02:57,740 --> 01:02:59,242
COME ON.

647
01:03:01,744 --> 01:03:03,746
OH, MAN, SORRY.

648
01:03:08,251 --> 01:03:10,253
[COUGHING]

649
01:03:10,253 --> 01:03:11,754
OH, MAN, SORRY.

650
01:03:12,255 --> 01:03:13,756
OK.

651
01:03:13,756 --> 01:03:15,758
THANK YOU.

652
01:03:26,519 --> 01:03:30,523
I'M NOT REALLY
SUPPOSED TO HAVE
ANY VISITORS, SO...

653
01:03:30,523 --> 01:03:33,025
Terry: WE REALLY DON'T HAVE
THE TIME, EITHER.

654
01:03:33,025 --> 01:03:35,027
HA HA HA! OK.

655
01:03:35,027 --> 01:03:37,029
YOU TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF, HUH?

656
01:03:37,530 --> 01:03:40,032
Pits: TAKE CARE.
GET WELL SOON.

657
01:03:40,032 --> 01:03:41,534
SEE YOU, GUYS.

658
01:03:42,034 --> 01:03:43,035
[DOOR OPENS]

659
01:03:43,536 --> 01:03:45,037
[DOOR CLOSES]

660
01:03:53,045 --> 01:03:55,548
WILL YOU DO
SOMETHING FOR ME?

661
01:03:55,548 --> 01:03:57,049
YES.

662
01:03:59,552 --> 01:04:01,554
THE NEXT TIME YOU COME,

663
01:04:01,554 --> 01:04:03,055
COULD YOU WEAR
SOMETHING MORE...

664
01:04:05,057 --> 01:04:07,059
MORE LOOSE...

665
01:04:09,562 --> 01:04:12,064
SO I, UH...

666
01:04:12,064 --> 01:04:14,567
SO I WON'T HAVE TO SEE
YOUR BODY.

667
01:04:36,839 --> 01:04:38,841
[SOBBING]

668
01:04:45,348 --> 01:04:47,350
[DOOR OPENS]

669
01:04:53,105 --> 01:04:56,108
BESS, YOU'LL
HAVE TO GO NOW

670
01:04:56,108 --> 01:04:58,110
BECAUSE JAN NEEDS
TO REST.

671
01:04:58,611 --> 01:05:00,112
ALL RIGHT.

672
01:05:08,120 --> 01:05:10,122
[DOOR CLOSES]

673
01:05:12,375 --> 01:05:14,877
YOU SHOULDN'T GET HIM
TOO OVEREMOTIONAL,
YOU KNOW.

674
01:05:14,877 --> 01:05:16,879
IT'S NOT GOOD FOR HIM.

675
01:05:16,879 --> 01:05:19,382
I'M SORRY.

676
01:05:19,382 --> 01:05:21,884
YOU GOT TO
CHEER HIM UP.

677
01:05:25,388 --> 01:05:27,390
IS HE ASLEEP NOW?

678
01:05:27,390 --> 01:05:29,392
WELL, HE SHOULD BE...

679
01:05:29,892 --> 01:05:31,894
THE AMOUNT
I'VE GIVEN HIM.

680
01:05:33,529 --> 01:05:35,031
WOULD IT BE
ALL RIGHT

681
01:05:35,031 --> 01:05:38,034
IF I WENT AND HAD
A LOOK AT HIM?

682
01:05:58,054 --> 01:06:00,556
I LOVE YOU, JAN.

683
01:06:09,065 --> 01:06:13,069
[IMITATING JAN]
I LOVE YOU,
TOO, BESS.

684
01:06:13,069 --> 01:06:16,572
YOU ARE THE LOVE
OF MY LIFE.

685
01:06:37,126 --> 01:06:39,128
BESS.

686
01:06:42,131 --> 01:06:44,133
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

687
01:06:44,133 --> 01:06:46,635
I'VE BEEN
TO THE CHURCH.

688
01:06:49,638 --> 01:06:52,141
WHAT, AT 2:00
IN THE MORNING?

689
01:06:58,147 --> 01:07:00,649
I DON'T WANT YOU
GETTING ILL AGAIN...

690
01:07:01,150 --> 01:07:02,651
LIKE YOU DID
WHEN SAM DIED.

691
01:07:02,651 --> 01:07:04,653
I SAID I'VE BEEN
TO THE CHURCH.

692
01:07:04,653 --> 01:07:06,655
IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THE CHURCH.

693
01:07:07,156 --> 01:07:10,159
DID YOU HEAR
WHAT I SAID? DID YOU?

694
01:07:11,660 --> 01:07:14,163
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO GET ILL AGAIN

695
01:07:14,163 --> 01:07:16,665
LIKE YOU DID
WHEN SAM DIED.

696
01:07:16,665 --> 01:07:20,169
I'VE HAD A WORD
WITH DR. RICHARDSON,
ALL RIGHT?

697
01:07:20,169 --> 01:07:23,172
AND HE SAYS
HE COULD SEE YOU TOMORROW.

698
01:07:23,172 --> 01:07:25,674
OH, CAN HE?

699
01:07:31,680 --> 01:07:33,182
[DOOR OPENS]

700
01:07:33,182 --> 01:07:36,185
BESS, WOULD YOU LIKE
TO COME IN?

701
01:07:49,698 --> 01:07:51,700
[DRAWER OPENS]

702
01:07:58,340 --> 01:08:00,843
DODO SAID
I HAD TO COME.

703
01:08:00,843 --> 01:08:04,713
SHE HAS THIS IDEA
ABOUT ME TREATING YOU.

704
01:08:07,716 --> 01:08:11,220
MY PREDECESSOR ADMITTED YOU
A FEW YEARS AGO.

705
01:08:12,221 --> 01:08:14,723
WELL, WHY DID HE
DO THAT?

706
01:08:15,224 --> 01:08:17,226
I DON'T KNOW.

707
01:08:17,226 --> 01:08:19,728
NO, NOR DO I.

708
01:08:19,728 --> 01:08:22,731
YOU WERE UPSET BECAUSE
YOUR BROTHER HAD DIED,

709
01:08:22,731 --> 01:08:26,485
AND NOW YOU'RE UPSET
BECAUSE YOUR HUSBAND'S ILL.

710
01:08:26,485 --> 01:08:28,487
NOTHING UNUSUAL
ABOUT THAT.

711
01:08:30,990 --> 01:08:33,993
AM I NOT GOING TO
HAVE SOME PILLS?

712
01:08:34,493 --> 01:08:36,495
I'M PROBABLY NOT LIKE
YOUR OLD DOCTOR.

713
01:08:36,495 --> 01:08:38,998
I DON'T THINK THAT PEOPLE
SHOULD BE GIVEN PILLS

714
01:08:38,998 --> 01:08:41,000
JUST BECAUSE THEY DO
WHAT'S ONLY NATURAL.

715
01:08:42,251 --> 01:08:45,254
MAYBE SHOWING WHAT YOU FEEL
ISN'T THE DONE THING

716
01:08:45,254 --> 01:08:46,755
FROM WHERE
YOU COME FROM,

717
01:08:46,755 --> 01:08:49,258
BUT IT'S CERTAINLY
NO DISEASE.

718
01:08:50,259 --> 01:08:53,262
WHAT...HAPPENED
ON THE RIG

719
01:08:53,262 --> 01:08:55,264
WAS MY FAULT.

720
01:08:56,765 --> 01:08:58,267
HOW COME?

721
01:09:00,269 --> 01:09:03,272
I PRAYED TO GOD
TO SEND HIM HOME.

722
01:09:05,774 --> 01:09:07,776
WELL...

723
01:09:11,280 --> 01:09:13,282
WELL...

724
01:09:13,282 --> 01:09:16,285
WHAT POWERS
YOU POSSESS.

725
01:09:16,285 --> 01:09:17,786
DO YOU REALLY...

726
01:09:18,287 --> 01:09:20,789
DO YOU REALLY BELIEVE
THAT YOU POSSESS
SUCH POWERS?

727
01:09:22,291 --> 01:09:26,178
I KNOW YOU PEOPLE BELIEVE
A LOT ABOUT YOURSELVES.

728
01:09:26,178 --> 01:09:27,680
BESS...

729
01:09:27,680 --> 01:09:30,182
PERHAPS YOU SHOULD DO
A BIT OF GRIEVING

730
01:09:30,182 --> 01:09:31,684
FOR YOURSELF
INSTEAD OF HIM.

731
01:09:32,184 --> 01:09:34,186
I THINK YOU SHOULD
COME AND SEE ME

732
01:09:34,186 --> 01:09:36,188
NOW AND AGAIN
IF YOU FEEL LIKE IT.

733
01:09:42,061 --> 01:09:44,063
I'M SORRY.

734
01:09:44,063 --> 01:09:45,564
OH. HA HA!

735
01:09:45,564 --> 01:09:47,066
COME ON.

736
01:09:49,068 --> 01:09:51,954
WELL, THINGS WILL PICK UP
ONCE HE GETS HOME AGAIN.

737
01:09:58,711 --> 01:10:00,713
??
T. Rex:
?? WELL, SHE'S MY WOMAN OF GOLD

738
01:10:00,713 --> 01:10:03,716
?? YES, SHE'S NOT VERY OLD,
UH-HUH, HUH ??

