OF THE BUS.

1001
01:31:16,904 --> 01:31:17,905
YEAH.

1002
01:31:17,905 --> 01:31:18,906
COME.

1003
01:31:22,910 --> 01:31:26,914
DODO. DODO.

1004
01:31:27,915 --> 01:31:29,917
JAN.

1005
01:31:30,418 --> 01:31:31,919
