1008
01:31:39,927 --> 01:31:41,929
ARE YOU AWAKE?

1009
01:31:44,432 --> 01:31:45,933
TALK TO ME.

1010
01:31:54,942 --> 01:31:56,444
HI, BESS.

1011
01:31:56,944 --> 01:31:59,447
