A CHAT WITH YOU.

1012
01:32:01,449 --> 01:32:02,950
BESS.

1013
01:32:06,454 --> 01:32:09,957
THIS IS MY BUS--MY BUS.

1014
01:34:59,126 --> 01:35:03,130
