1057
01:39:44,194 --> 01:39:48,198
DON'T GET YOUR HOPES
UP TOO HIGH, WILL YOU?

1058
01:39:48,198 --> 01:39:51,702
DR. RICHARDSON SAYS
THAT JAN COULD GET
WORSE AGAIN.

1059
01:39:53,203 --> 01:39:56,206
I'M THE ONE
WHO SAVED HIS LIFE.

1060
01:39:56,206 --> 01:39:58,208
I CAN SAVE IT AGAIN.

1061
01:39:58,709 --> 01:40:02,713
BESS, WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

1062
01:40:02,713 --> 01:40:08,218
I TOLD JAN STORIES--
