1064
01:40:13,724 --> 01:40:16,226
YOU SEE,
LOVE CAN SAVE JAN.

1065
01:40:16,226 --> 01:40:18,729
HE MUST NOT FORGET
ABOUT LOVE.

1066
01:40:18,729 --> 01:40:20,230
HE TOLD ME THAT.

1067
01:40:20,230 --> 01:40:23,233
HE TELLS ME
WHAT TO DO.

1068
01:40:23,734 --> 01:40:26,236
BESS, I'M GLAD THAT
YOU LISTENED TO JAN,

1069
01:40:26,236 --> 01:40:29,239
BUT DON'T LET HIM GAIN
TOO MUCH POWER OVER YOU.

1070
01:40:29,239 --> 01:40:31,492
SICKNESS IS
A MIGHTY POWER.

1071
01:40:31,492 --> 01:40:32,993
I'VE SAVED JAN.

1072
01:40:32,993 --> 01:40:35,996
