IT'S STUPID!

1073
01:40:37,498 --> 01:40:40,000
YOU ALWAYS SAID
THAT I WASN'T STUPID.

1074
01:40:40,000 --> 01:40:42,503
WELL, YOU'RE STUPID
IF YOU SAY THINGS
LIKE THAT.

1075
01:40:43,003 --> 01:40:45,139
WHY ARE YOU SAYING
I'M STUPID NOW?

1076
01:40:45,139 --> 01:40:47,641
BECAUSE I CAN SEE
THAT YOU'RE DISAPPEARING

1077
01:40:47,641 --> 01:40:49,143
INTO A WORLD
OF MAKE-BELIEVE,

1078
01:40:49,143 --> 01:40:51,145
AND IT WORRIES ME.

1079
01:40:51,145 --> 01:40:52,646
I USED TO GO MAD

1080
01:40:52,646 --> 01:40:54,148
WHEN PEOPLE
CALLED YOU STUPID,

1081
01:40:54,148 --> 01:40:57,434
STUPID.
BUT YOU

1082
