Dr. Richardson:
WE'RE GOING TO PUT
A DRAIN IN THIS AFTERNOON.

1083
01:41:01,939 --> 01:41:05,943
IT'LL BE MUCH EASIER
TO GET THROUGH TO HIM.

1084
01:41:05,943 --> 01:41:08,946
DON'T WORRY.
IT'S A VERY MINOR OPERATION.

1085
01:41:10,447 --> 01:41:14,451
Jan: ARE YOU TRYING
TO MAKE ME FEEL GUILTY?

1086
01:41:14,451 --> 01:41:16,954
Bess: WHAT
MAKES YOU SAY THAT?

1087
01:41:21,341 --> 01:41:24,845
I THINK SHE'S TRYING
TO MAKE ME FEEL GUILTY.

1088
01:41:31,351 --> 01:41:32,853
[JAN SIGHS]

1089
01:41:32,853 --> 01:41:34,354
COME HERE.

1090
01:41:40,110 --> 01:41:42,112
YOU LOOK FUCKING AWFUL.

1091
01:41:46,617 --> 01:41:48,735
WHY DO YOU DRESS
LIKE THAT?

1092
01:41:52,239 --> 01:41:55,742
YOU DRESS LIKE A WIDOW.

1093
01:41:55,742 --> 01:41:58,495
I'M NOT EVEN DEAD YET.

1094
01:42:01,498 --> 01:42:04,001
MAYBE YOU WISH I WAS.

1095
01:42:04,001 --> 01:42:05,886
NO. NO, NO.

1096
01:42:05,886 --> 01:42:09,256
YOU HAVEN'T DONE
WHAT I ASKED YOU TO DO.

1097
01:42:09,256 --> 01:42:10,757
I HAVE!

1098
01:42:10,757 --> 01:42:13,760
I ASKED YOU
TO BE WITH A MAN.

1099
01:42:14,261 --> 01:42:15,762
I HAVE DONE THAT.

1100
01:42:15,762 --> 01:42:18,765
YOU CALL THAT
BEING WITH A MAN?

1101
01:42:18,765 --> 01:42:20,767
I CALL IT A JOKE.

1102
01:42:26,773 --> 01:42:31,161
I LOVE YOU.
I DON'T LOVE
SOME OTHER MAN.

1103
01:42:33,163 --> 01:42:34,665
PROVE IT.

1104
01:42:41,038 --> 01:42:43,040
BESS, WHAT IS GOING ON?

1105
01:42:43,040 --> 01:42:48,545
ARE YOU SLEEPING
WITH OTHER MEN
TO FEED HIS SICK FANTASIES?

1106
01:42:48,545 --> 01:42:50,547
HE DID GET BETTER.

1107
01:42:50,547 --> 01:42:53,050
NO, HE DID NOT
GET BETTER!

1108
01:42:53,050 --> 01:42:54,551
THAT'S JUST THE WAY
IT GOES, BESS.

1109
01:42:54,551 --> 01:42:56,553
SOMETIMES HE'S BETTER;
SOMETIMES HE'S WORSE.

1110
01:42:56,553 --> 01:43:00,057
IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH WHAT YOU'RE DOING.
THAT'S ALL IN YOUR MIND.

1111
01:43:00,057 --> 01:43:04,561
HE IS MY HUSBAND,
AND GOD HAS SAID
THAT I MUST HONOR HIM.

1112
01:43:04,561 --> 01:43:06,063
WELL, IF THAT'S WHAT
HONORING IS ALL ABOUT,

1113
01:43:06,063 --> 01:43:08,565
THEN I MUST HAVE
SOMETHING WRONG.

1114
01:43:08,565 --> 01:43:11,068
WELL, YOU DON'T COME
FROM AROUND HERE,
DO YOU?

1115
01:43:11,568 --> 01:43:13,570
NO, AND I'M GLAD
I DON'T.

1116
01:43:13,570 --> 01:43:17,074
WITH LOCALS TALKING--
IT MAKES ME SICK.

1117
01:43:17,074 --> 01:43:20,077
BUT YOU LIVE HERE,
AND YOU GO
TO THE CHURCH.

1118
01:43:20,077 --> 01:43:24,581
YES, BUT IT DON'T MEAN
I DON'T LOOK AT THINGS
ME OWN WAY.

1119
01:43:24,581 --> 01:43:27,584
WHY DON'T YOU
MOVE, THEN?
YOUR HUSBAND'S DEAD.

1120
01:43:29,336 --> 01:43:32,339
YOU KNOW VERY WELL
WHY I DON'T MOVE.

1121
01:43:32,339 --> 01:43:34,841
I DON'T MOVE
BECAUSE OF YOU.

1122
01:43:34,841 --> 01:43:38,845
A WOMAN HAS TO CHOOSE
FOR HERSELF, BESS.

1123
01:43:38,845 --> 01:43:41,848
SHE HAS TO HAVE
A MIND OF HER OWN.

1124
01:43:42,349 --> 01:43:46,353
NOW, WHAT YOU'RE DOING
IS MAKING THINGS WORSE.
IT'S NONSENSE.

1125
01:43:46,353 --> 01:43:47,854
HIS HEAD'S FULL OF SCARS.

1126
01:43:47,854 --> 01:43:49,356
HE'S UP TO HIS EYEBALLS
IN DRUGS.

1127
01:43:49,856 --> 01:43:50,857
HE DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S SAYING.

1128
01:43:52,743 --> 01:43:54,745
AND HE DOESN'T KNOW.

1129
01:43:59,750 --> 01:44:00,751
I'M SORRY.

1130
01:44:02,753 --> 01:44:04,755
I'M SORRY.

1131
01:44:06,940 --> 01:44:09,443
[MEEK VOICE]
AM I GOING TO GO TO HELL?

1132
01:44:09,443 --> 01:44:16,450
[FIRM VOICE]
WHOM DO YOU WANT TO SAVE--
YOURSELF OR JAN?

1133
01:44:20,070 --> 01:44:21,071
BESS.

1134
01:44:21,071 --> 01:44:23,573
[TURNS VACUUM OFF]

1135
01:44:23,573 --> 01:44:27,077
IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME--
MOST UNLIKE YOU.

1136
01:44:30,080 --> 01:44:33,083
Minister: I MUST
WARN YOU THAT THE LORD
LOOKS WITH ANGER

1137
01:44:33,333 --> 01:44:35,335
UPON THOSE WHO FAIL HIM.

1138
01:44:37,838 --> 01:44:40,340
[TURNS VACUUM ON]

1139
01:44:49,733 --> 01:44:52,736
YOU'VE GOT TO LEND ME
SOMETHING TO WEAR.

1140
01:44:55,105 --> 01:44:57,107
[MEN TALKING]

1141
01:45:18,628 --> 01:45:20,130
Man: A GOOD SHOT.

1142
01:45:29,139 --> 01:45:31,141
Man: ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT.

1143
01:45:32,776 --> 01:45:34,277
[POOL BALLS CLICK]

1144
01:45:42,285 --> 01:45:43,787
HELLO.

1145
01:45:48,291 --> 01:45:49,793
Man: GOOD SHOT.

1146
01:45:54,297 --> 01:45:55,799
HOW MUCH, DARLING?

1147
01:46:06,059 --> 01:46:08,428
