1148
01:46:08,428 --> 01:46:10,430
OK. GOOD.

1149
01:46:15,819 --> 01:46:17,320
[MONITOR BEEPING]

1150
01:46:25,445 --> 01:46:26,947
Man: THANK YOU.

1151
