Dodo: I CAN'T HEAR
THE BLOOD PRESSURE.

1152
01:46:32,452 --> 01:46:34,454
THE BLOOD PRESSURE.

1153
01:46:34,704 --> 01:46:36,706
WE HAVE
A FIBRILLATION.

1154
01:46:41,962 --> 01:46:44,965
CLEAR.

1155
01:46:44,965 --> 01:46:46,967
Dodo: STILL NO CHANGE.

1156
01:46:47,217 --> 01:46:49,719
OK. CLEAR.

1157
01:46:53,723 --> 01:46:55,725
CLEAR AGAIN,
PLEASE.

1158
01:46:59,112 --> 01:47:00,113
GO ON.

1159
01:47:00,113 --> 01:47:03,116
CLEAR, PLEASE.

1160
01:47:03,116 --> 01:47:04,618
[MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY]

1161
01:47:04,618 --> 01:47:05,619
YES!

1162
01:47:05,619 --> 01:47:06,620
OH, YES!

1163
01:47:06,620 --> 01:47:08,121
ALL RIGHT.

1164
01:47:10,624 --> 01:47:12,125
GOOD WORK.
GOOD WORK.

1165
01:47:12,626 --> 01:47:14,628
IT'S OK?

