SIMPLE OPERATION.

1177
01:48:28,902 --> 01:48:31,404
AS YOU KNOW. WELL,

1178
01:48:33,290 --> 01:48:35,292
I SHOULDN'T
HAVE TO SAY THAT.

1179
01:48:35,292 --> 01:48:36,793
YOU KNOW THAT
VERY WELL.

1180
01:48:41,798 --> 01:48:44,801
Mother: I WANT
A WORD WITH BESS
ON HER OWN.

1181
01:48:50,056 --> 01:48:52,058
THANK YOU, DOROTHY.

1182
01:48:53,560 --> 01:48:57,063
I'M NOT GOING TO ASK YOU
WHAT YOU'VE BEEN
GETTING UP TO

1183
01:48:57,063 --> 01:48:59,566
