AS YOU ARE LIVING
UNDER MY ROOF,

1185
01:49:03,069 --> 01:49:06,573
YOU ARE TO BEHAVE
LIKE A DECENT HUMAN BEING.

1186
01:49:06,573 --> 01:49:09,075
I HAVE NEVER
LIED TO YOU.

1187
01:49:09,576 --> 01:49:11,194
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

1188
01:49:15,198 --> 01:49:16,700
YES, MOTHER.

1189
01:49:20,203 --> 01:49:23,206
THIS IS VERY PAINFUL
FOR ME.

1190
01:49:23,707 --> 01:49:25,709
YOUR GRANDFATHER
CAN NO LONGER

1191
01:49:25,709 --> 01:49:28,712
