OUT OF YOUR CONTROL.

1213
01:51:01,304 --> 01:51:03,807
HAVE I?

1214
01:51:05,809 --> 01:51:07,811
COME ON, BESS.

1215
01:51:07,811 --> 01:51:10,313
YOU'RE NOT
A KID ANYMORE.

1216
01:51:10,313 --> 01:51:12,315
LOOK,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE,

1217
01:51:12,315 --> 01:51:13,817
HE'S FORCING YOU
TO GET SCREWED

1218
01:51:14,317 --> 01:51:15,819
BY EVERY TOM,
DICK, AND HARRY.

1219
